PreRequisits:

 Windows:

pacman -S mingw-w64-i686-gtk3 mingw-w64-i686-python2-gobject 
mingw-w64-i686-python3-gobject

Linux (ubuntu / debian):

sudo apt install python-gi python-gi-cairo python3-gi python3-gi-cairo 
gir1.2-gtk-3.0

Linux (Fedora):

sudo dnf install pygobject3 python3-gobject gtk3

Linux (Arch)

sudo pacman -S python-gobject python2-gobject gtk3


openSUSE

sudo zypper install python-gobject python3-gobject gtk3

macOS

brew install pygobject3 --with-python@2 gtk+3




